The evidence with the title 'UAW planning 'buy american' cars campaign -- easier said than ... ' says Feb 16, 2017  ... With a populist , protectionist president in the White House, the president of the United Auto Workers thinks it's time to revive the "Buy American"  ... Most automakers have concluded they ca n't afford to make small passenger cars in the U.S., so their factories here churn out mostly expensive trucks and SUVs. 
